snippet.title: Trine 2: Goblin Menace Gamescom 2012 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trine 2: Goblin Menace Trailer

Trine 2: Goblin Menace is an all new campaign spanning six unique levels, further improving the award-winning visuals of the original Trine 2. In addition, Goblin Menace features new revolutionary skills that are also playable in the original game.

For more information, please visit:

http://trine2.com
http://frozenbyte.com/press/press_trine2_gm.php
